title: Sam's Blog # 1 CWC Scotland '10
description: Sam Lamiroy is blogging during the O'Neill Cold Water Classic in Scotland. In his first blog he shows his roadtrip from his home ending in Thurso for the most northern surf contest in the world, O'Neill Cold Water Classic Scotland 2010
